@BellaBella; seeding is hosting and increasing the download speed for other users. You can seed by simply leaving your torrent application over when the torrent has completed downloading.

This is how you register.

Open up the keygen (located in keygen.rar, I believe..).
Open up Photoshop, it should ask you to activate your version of Photoshop CS3, activate it and enter the "Serial" that the keygen gave you. (Mine was 1330-1089-1984-0801-5387-0863)
Once you have done that, it should say it failed and you need to activate it via a few options. Select the phone option, it should give you a few numbers. Copy the "serial" number that Photoshop CS3 phone activation gave you. Paste that in the "Response" box on the keygen. Once you have done that, copy the "Activation code" in the keygen and paste it into Photoshop CS3, and you're done!
Thank you. I'll see if this torrent works or not...I'll write a review about it later. Thanks for now, SilentWulf.
